oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Welcome Back Nashville's Christmas
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Christmas; Gill, Vince; Grant, Amy; Holidays; Metal photoplates; Smith, Michael W. (Michael Whitaker), 1957-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and green on white) announcing Nashville's Christmas concert with Amy Grant, Vince Gill, Michael W. Smith and the Nashville Symphony Orchestra at the Gaylord Entertainment Center on December 5 and 6. Poster features metal photoplates of Amy Grant, Vince Gill, and Michael W. Smith.
